BEWARE: WS_SIZE (below) should *always* be the size of ws (above)

@= decl
@:@1_decl_ws(WS_SIZE, 32)@
@:@1_decl_ws(QNAME,    2)@
@:@1_decl_ws(BOOL,     3)@
@:@1_decl_ws(INT,      4)@
